title: New Jawa 42 FJ350 launched at Rs 1,99,142 : Check specifications, mileage, engine details
description: Jawa 42 FJ350 launch: Jawa Yezdi Motorcycles has launched the new Jawa 42 FJ350 at Rs 1,99,142 (Delhi ex-showroom). Named after founder František Janeček, this model features a 334-cc engine, six-gear transmission, and various enhancements. The company plans to open 100 new stores nationwide before the festive season, positioning the bike to compete with Royal Enfield 350.
